# Forecaster agent parameters for Santa Fe Stockmarket.
# Parameters are recognized solely by position within file -- watch out

# This file is only used by those forecasting agents that don't have
# a more specialized parameter file of their own.  Presently LI.

# Rule-related parameters
1	# numfcasts -- number of forecasts per agent
500.0	# tauv -- moving average healing time for variances
5.0	# lambda -- risk aversion parameter
1.0	# maxbid -- maximum bid or offer
0.001	# beta -- strength scaling Boltzmann parameter
